Package: getgrib
Type: Package
Title: Getting Data from Grib Files using R via ecCodes
Version: 2.0-3
Date: 2018-12-12
Author: Reto Stauffer
Maintainer: Reto Stauffer <reto.stauffer@uibk.ac.at>
Description: Provides a set of methods and function to read data from grib1 and
    grib2 files based on the ECMWF ecCodes library. Developed on ecCodes Version
    2.9.2. One of the core functions is the interpolate method which allows to
    perform bilinear and inverse distance weighting and nearest neighbour
    interpolation for a set of stations/locations.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), raster, sp
Suggetsts: zoo
License: GPL-2
